'''Digit droids''' were [[Droid/Legends|droids]] primarily used in the game [[Digotto]]. They were round and red, with a black center that displayed a number. The game of Digotto was based on mathematics. [[Teemto Pagalies/Legends|Teemto Pagalies]] was allegedly fond of this game, and described the droids as "cute."

